<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <!-- The above 3 meta tags *must* come first in the head; any other head content must come *after* these tags -->
    <title>SiteContact</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/prism.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- HTML5 shim and Respond.js for IE8 support of HTML5 elements and media queries -->
    <!-- WARNING: Respond.js doesn't work if you view the page via file:// -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
      <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4" align="center" style="top:20px;">
        <img src="/img/logo.png" height="160px" width="160px">
        <h1>Форма обратной связи для Вашего сайта</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3" style="top:40px;">
      Сервис не требует регистрации, чтобы начать получать сообщения через форму, укажите Ваш адрес электронной почты, а затем используйте полученный html код на своей странице:   
        <form id="signup" action="/signup" method="POST">

          <div class="form-group form-group-lg">
            <label for="email"></label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="hello@mail.ru">
          </div>

          <pre>
          <code class="language-html">
            &#60;form method="POST" action="//sitecontact.ru/<span id="emailAddress"></span>"&#62;             
            &#60;input type="text" name="имя" &#62;             
            &#60;input type="email" name="email" &#62;             
            &#60;button type="submit" value="Отправить"&#62;
            &#60;/form&#62;             
          </code>
          </pre>
          <button type="submit" style="width:100%;" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Подключить почтовый ящик</button>

        </form>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- jQuery (necessary for Bootstrap's JavaScript plugins) -->
    <!-- Include all compiled plugins (below), or include individual files as needed -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/prism.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    document.getElementById('email').onkeyup = function(e){
      document.getElementById('emailAddress').innerText = e.target.value; 
    }  
    </script>
  </body>
</html>